Package io.github.m0pt0pmatt.survivalgames.task

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Task
    A unit of work which is performed on a SurvivalGame.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CleanStateTask  
    ClearPlayersTask
    Clears players and spectators from the game.
    ClearWorldBorderTask
    Resets the WorldBorder to a very long distance.
    CreateCageSnapshotsTask  
    CreateDeathmatchBorderTask
    Creates the smaller world border for the deathmatch.
    CreateWorldBorderTask
    Creates the world border from the survival game
    DelayedTask
    A Task which is delayed before it is executed.
    FillChestsTask
    Fills chests with items.
    RestoreBlocksTask
    Sets the blocks in the map
    StartEventIntervalsTask
    Starts the event intervals, which will continuously fire events.
    StartMobSpawnersTask
    Starts the mob spawners, which will spawn entities continuously.
    StopEventIntervalsTask
    Stops the event intervals.
    StopMobSpawnersTask
    Stops the mob spawners.
    UpdateScoreBoardTask
    Updates a player's scoreboard with the current players and their kill counts.
